msgid ""
"After each successful send, create a ZFS bookmark as the incremental base. "
"Allows pruning source snapshots to 1 while maintaining incremental "
"replication. Not compatible with 'Recursive' (ZFS does not support recursive"
" sends from a bookmark) and not needed when 'Use existing snapshots' is "
"enabled."
msgstr "After each successful send, create a ZFS bookmark as the incremental base. Allows pruning source snapshots to 1 while maintaining incremental replication. Not compatible with 'Recursive' (ZFS does not support recursive sends from a bookmark) and not needed when 'Use existing snapshots' is enabled."

