msgid ""
"Are you sure? For a mirror or stripe pool this attaches the new device to "
"the selected existing device, extending the mirror or converting a stripe "
"device into a 2-way mirror (irreversible without full pool recreation). For "
"a RAIDZ pool this expands the selected RAIDZ vdev by adding one device, "
"permanently increasing its width."
msgstr "Are you sure? For a mirror or stripe pool this attaches the new device to the selected existing device, extending the mirror or converting a stripe device into a 2-way mirror (irreversible without full pool recreation). For a RAIDZ pool this expands the selected RAIDZ vdev by adding one device, permanently increasing its width."

