msgid ""
"Do not create a new snapshot. Instead, replicate the most recent existing "
"snapshot matching the prefix. Use this when a separate snapshot job already "
"manages snapshots for this dataset — this is the recommended approach when "
"replicating to multiple destinations or at different frequencies, as it "
"avoids conflicts between replication chains."
msgstr "Do not create a new snapshot. Instead, replicate the most recent existing snapshot matching the prefix. Use this when a separate snapshot job already manages snapshots for this dataset — this is the recommended approach when replicating to multiple destinations or at different frequencies, as it avoids conflicts between replication chains."

