"replication jobs share the same dataset and prefix — prefer 0 and manage "
"retention with a dedicated snapshot job instead. Ignored when 'Use existing "
"snapshots' is enabled."
msgstr "Number of replication snapshots to keep on the source after each successful send. 0 = keep all. Source pruning can break incremental chains if multiple replication jobs share the same dataset and prefix — prefer 0 and manage retention with a dedicated snapshot job instead. Ignored when 'Use existing snapshots' is enabled."

